title: The Led Zeppelin Chamber Suite
description:
The Classic Rock String Quartet - The Led Zeppelin Chamber Suite

The songs of Led Zeppelin, one of Britain's greatest hard rock bands, are given a new twist in this concert video. The Classic Rock Quartet: Tribute to Led Zeppelin features ten of the group's best-known songs arranged for a small classical ensemble featuring grand piano and three string players. Selections include "Dazed and Confused," "Kashmir,""Achilles' Last Stand," "Thank You," and "Stairway to Heaven."

Screen Ratio: Alternate Wide Screen (1.78:1)
Audio Tracks: Dolby Digital 5.1, Dolby Digital Stereo, DTS 5.1
Running time: 57 mins
